            "reset": "",
            "routine": "<p>(1 action) Prisoners trample toward the exit, dealing @Damage[(2d10+9)[bludgeoning]|options:area-damage] damage to each living creature in area <strong>K9</strong> and the hallway north of it (@Check[reflex|dc:25|basic] save). On a critical failure, the creature's grasp on anything it's carrying is weakened as if the hazard succeeded on a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Disarm] attempt. If its grasp was already weakened, they drop the item.</p><p><strong>Special</strong> If the PCs have not defeated the hazard after 4 rounds, it automatically ends as all the prisoners escape.</p>"
